to", "founders", "board"]}, {"id": "culture", "messages": ["Our employees are central to advancing our mission to revolutionize commerce and create value for our stakeholders.<br>We believe that investing in our global workforce is crucial for the sustained success of our business and strive to continue fostering a workplace that serves and empowers all our people to do the best work of their lives. Find out more information on our <a href="https://about.pypl.com/how-we-work/employees-and-culture/default.aspx" target="_blank">Employees & Culture</a> and <a href="https://about.pypl.com/our-impact/Communities/default.aspx" target="_blank">Our Impact – Communities</a> pages."], "label": "Employees & Culture", "image": "https://static.vscdn.net/images/careers/demo/eightfolddemo-pcsx-demo/1731687603::paypal+emp+and+culture", "url": "https://about.pypl.com/how-we-work/employees-and-culture/default.aspx", "keywords": ["culture", "workplace", "remote", "diversity", "environment", "employees"]}, {"id": "mission", "messages": ["We are revolutionizing commerce globally. With this mission as our North Star, we are aligned around one central vision: to make sending and receiving money, selling, and shopping simple, personalized, and secure.", "Our beliefs are the foundation for how we conduct business every day."], "label": "Mission & Values", "image": "https://static.vscdn.net/images/careers/demo/eightfolddemo-pcsx-demo/1731687745::paypal+mission", "url": "https://about.pypl.com/who-we-are/mission-vision-values/default.aspx", "keywords": ["mision", "values", "beliefs"]}, {"id": "business_ethics", "messages": ["Preserving our customers’ trust is paramount to our values and success"], "label": "Responsible Business Practices", "url": "https://about.pypl.com/how-we-work/responsible-business-practices/default.aspx", "image": "https://static.vscdn.net/images/careers/demo/eightfolddemo-pcsx-demo/1731687931::paypal+business+ethics", "keywords": ["ethics", "risk and compliance", "business conduct", "innovation", "social responsibility"]}, {"id": "faq-0", "messages": ["Graduate roles typically post for applications in the early fall. Periodically, additional roles may be added throughout the winter and spring seasons. 
