  <a href="https://paypal.eightfold.ai/careers/join?domain=paypal.com" target="_blank">here</a>!"], "label": "When does PayPal post internship opportunities?", "keywords": ["internship opportunities", "internship posting", "student hiring", "fall internship", "spring internship"]}, {"id": "faq-2", "messages": ["Interns receive a standard technology bundle which will include all equipment needed to perform their best work. This includes a company laptop and other assets/working equipment."], "label": "Will PayPal provide me a laptop or equipment during an internship?", "keywords": ["internship equipment", "laptop", "tech bundle", "company assets", "work tools"]}, {"id": "faq-3", "messages": ["PayPal’s Global Internship Program integrates interns into PayPal’s culture by introducing our core values of inclusion, wellness, innovation, and collaboration from day one and throughout the intern experience. Our interns are encouraged to grow through targeted learning and career pathing sessions, 1:1 mentorship, meaningful project work, and intern networking events. Some of the events our interns can look forward to include the Executive Speaker Series with PayPal’s CEO and other members of CEO Staff, Impact Day where interns worldwide give back to their local communities, enterprise hackathons, and our PayPal Intern Day celebration! Find out more <a href="https://careers.pypl.com/university-hiring/university-overview/default.aspx" target="_blank">here</a>."], "label": "What kind of activities will I get to participate in as an intern?", "keywords": ["intern activities", "mentorship", "hackathons", "intern events", "career sessions"]}, {"id": "faq-4", "messages": ["Interns in North America, India, China and Singapore are traditionally required to work 40 hours a week, unless otherwise stated in the offer letter. Working hours requirements in Europe and Latin America vary by country."], "label": "How many hours a week do interns work?", "keywords": ["intern hours", "weekly schedule", "work hours", "full-time internship"]}, {"id": "faq-5", "messages": ["No. At PayPal, we believe in life-work integration and therefore support our interns through a hybrid working model, which means that all interns have the flexibility to work between their home and in an office with their team."], "label": "Does PayPal offer remote internships?", "keywords": ["remote internships", "hybrid model", "work from home", "virtual internship"]}, {"id": "faq-6", "messages": ["Thank you for your interest in joining PayPal!  Our recruiting team is actively reviewing applicants and will be in touch will candidates selected to move forward in the interview process.  You can always check your status in your candidate profile too."], "label": "I completed the online application, but haven’t received a response. Am I still being considered or can I schedule an interview?", "keywords": ["application status", "interview", "candidate profile", "no response", "application follow-up"], "url": "https://paypal.eightfold.ai/candidate/login?domain=paypal.com"}, {"id": "faq-7", "messages": ["Thank you for reaching out and for your interest in a career at PayPal, we appreciate your email! Unfortunately, your application cannot be considered through this inbox. If you haven’t done so already, the best way to join our team is to visit our career site and use our job search tool to apply directly for a position that interests you. Good luck and thank you for your interest in joining our team."], "label": "I've provided my resume via this email can you please consider my application?", "keywords": ["resume submission", "email application", "apply online", "application process"], "url": "https://www.paypal.com/jobs"}, {"id": "faq-8", "messages": ["Thank you for reaching out to us and for your interest in a career at PayPal.  We recommend trying another browser and clearing your cache, then trying again."], "label": "Why am I not able to submit my application?", "keywords": ["application error", "submission issue", "technical problem", "browser cache"]}, {"id": "faq-9", "messages": ["Hi there, Thanks for your inquiry. Depending on when you had applied, the recruiter may have already begun the interview process with candidates that had applied prior to you.  There may have been some nuances that the hiring manager was looking for as well. We do appreciate your interest in us though and hope this helps to explain."], "label": "Why was I not selected for a role?", "keywords": ["not selected", "rejection reason", "hiring decision", "role fit"]}, {"id": "faq-10", "messages": ["Thank you for contacting PayPal Global Talent Acquisition.  I am sorry to hear you are experiencing issues. For customer support please use the Contact PayPal link located at https://www.paypal.com/selfhelp/home. You may receive a reply from our bot with information we hope will be helpful. If you need to communicate with a Representative, please work through/click on the links the bot offers until your message is moved to a queue where a Representative will be able to see it and reply. They will respond as soon as possible."], "label": "How can I get help with my PayPal account?", "url": "https://www.paypal.com/us/cshelp/personal", "keywords": ["PayPal support", "account help", "customer service", "self-help"]}, {"id": "faq-11", "messages": ["Thank you for contacting PayPal Global Talent Acquisition. Can you please reach out to our Employee Central HR team (employeecentralcases@paypal.com) with your data deletion request."], "label": "How can I get my data deleted?", "keywords": ["data deletion", "privacy", "remove my data", "GDPR", "HR request"], "url": "mailto:employeecentralcases@paypal.com"}, {"id": "faq-12", "messages": ["The best approach is to have the employee submit an Employee Referral Program ticket requesting to update the source of your application(s) to themselves an Employee Referral. They can submit the ticket by going onto PayPal’s HR ticketing system and searchi